reviewText: Ok, so it's from the 50s, but this so unoriginal.  I quit watching.
We haven't watched all the episodes yet but I feel this was way before it's time in the pace of the episodes and the comedy. I love Betty White, all of her work is perfection!
I bought this for my 38 year old daughter and she loves them.  She is a big fan of old movies and tv shows and absolutely loves Betty White so this is definitely for her.  Glad I bought it for her.
